  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a large skillet over low heat.",
    "Add the sliced scallions and cook for 2 minutes, or until they start to soften.",
    "Add the mushrooms and cook for 3-4 minutes, or until they release their liquid and start to brown.",
    "Add the miso paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the plum jam and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the soba noodles, soy sauce, sake, and pickled mustard greens. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger. Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, or until the noodles are well coated with the sauce.",
    "Season with salt-free seasoning blend to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional scallions if desired."
  ],
